longBusinessSummary: Image International Group, Inc. engages in the lead-zinc mining activities. The company was formerly known as Owlhead Minerals Corp. and changed its name to Image International Group, Inc. in December 2014. Image International Group, Inc. was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Blaine, Washington.
